{"title":"金色的日子","authors":["李勇"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":1,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"金色的日子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李勇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金色的日子姗姗来临"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是收获的季节"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田野弥漫太阳浓烈的气味"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成熟芳芬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风从蓝蓝的天空敛翅而下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满是尘土的脸上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咸涩的盐粒发着光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪烁从春到夏的艰辛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总是年复一年地期待"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"希冀是一支五彩的歌谣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚韧地引导播种和耕耘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一种幸福自心底漾起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在棉桃的银铃儿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与阳光碰响的喜讯里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沉默如粒粒饱满的谷子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深沉而愉快地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回味生活的真情＊"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}